text: Sanaya Irani (born 17 September 1983) is an Indian actress. She is known for playing Gunjan in Miley Jab Hum Tum, Khushi in Iss Pyaar Ko Kya Naam Doon? and Parvati in Rangrasiya. == References == == Other websites == * * * Category:1983 births Category:Living people Category:Indian actors
title: Sanaya Irani
